<html><h1 style="margin-top:16px"><span style="font-size:16pt"><span style="color:#2e74b5"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style='font-family:"Calibri Light",sans-serif'><span style="font-weight:normal">View metrics collected using Connector for SCOM (2020.05) as reports on BVD</span></span></span></span></span></h1>

<h1 style="margin-top:16px"><span style="font-size:16pt"><span style="color:#2e74b5"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style='font-family:"Calibri Light",sans-serif'><span style="font-weight:normal">Prerequisites</span></span></span></span></span></h1>

<ul>
	<li style="margin-left:8px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="color:black">OpsB Suite 2020.08 should be installed</span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="margin-left:8px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="color:black">OBM 2020.05 should be installed.</span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="margin-left:8px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="color:black">Certificate exchange between the OBM and COSO Data Lake should be done.</span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="margin-left:8px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="color:black">BVD should be connected to COSO Data Lake.</span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="margin-left:8px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="color:black">The Connector for SCOM should be installed and configured on the managed node.</span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>

<h1 style="margin-top:16px"><span style="font-size:16pt"><span style="color:#2e74b5"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style='font-family:"Calibri Light",sans-serif'><span style="font-weight:normal">Task 1: Install report content package</span></span></span></span></span></h1>
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>Download and install report content package. For more information, see <a style="color:blue; text-decoration:underline" href="https://docs.microfocus.com/itom/Connector_for_Microsoft_SCOM:2020.05/COSO#Install_report_content_package">Install report content package</a>.</span></span></span>

<h1 style="margin-top:16px"><span style="font-size:16pt"><span style="color:#2e74b5"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style='font-family:"Calibri Light",sans-serif'><span style="font-weight:normal">Task 2: Deploy the OpsCx for SCOM - Store Once aspect</span></span></span></span></span></h1>

<ol>
	<li style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:19px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:list .5in"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">Click&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Administration</span></strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Monitoring</span></strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Management Templates &amp; Aspects</span></strong>.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:19px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:list .5in"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">In the&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Configuration Folders</span></strong>&nbsp;pane, expand&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Operations Connector</span></strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>SCOM</span></strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Aspects</span></strong>.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:19px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:list .5in"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">In the&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Management Templates &amp; Aspects</span></strong>&nbsp;pane, select the&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>OpsCx for SCOM - Store Once</span></strong>&nbsp;aspect, and then click&nbsp;</span></span></span><a style="color:blue; text-decoration:underline" href="https://docs.microfocus.com/itomw/Connector_for_Microsoft_SCOM:2020.05/COSO"><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#3a83e6"><span style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-underline:none"><img style="width:16px; height:16px" alt="SQL 2018.06 MPTools.PNG" src="/mediawiki/images/pn_images/pn_image_5f23a85c02f792.72425774.png"></span></span></span></span></span>&nbsp;</a><strong><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">Assign and Deploy Item</span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:19px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:list .5in"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">In the&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Configuration Item</span></strong>&nbsp;tab, select the managed node where the connector for SCOM is running to deploy the aspect.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:19px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:list .5in"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">Click&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Next</span></strong>.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:19px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:list .5in"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">In the&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Required Parameters</span></strong>&nbsp;tab, select the value for the&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Target Server</span></strong>&nbsp;parameter. Follow the steps below:</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>
	<ol style="list-style-type:lower-alpha">
		<li style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:15px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">Select the&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Target Server</span></strong>&nbsp;parameter and click&nbsp;</span></span></span><a style="color:blue; text-decoration:underline" href="https://docs.microfocus.com/itomw/Connector_for_Microsoft_SCOM:2020.05/COSO"><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#3a83e6"><span style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-underline:none"><img style="width:16px; height:16px" alt="SQL 2018.06 MPPencil.PNG" src="/mediawiki/images/pn_images/pn_image_5f23a85c65cf74.45613702.png"></span></span></span></span></span>&nbsp;</a><strong><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">Edit</span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
		<li style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:15px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">In the&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Edit Parameter&nbsp;</span></strong>window, select the&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Value</span></strong>&nbsp;radio button and enter the endpoint URL.<br>
		For example, https://&lt;OBM FQDN&gt;:36500/itomdi/receiver.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
		<li style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:15px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">Click&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>OK</span></strong>.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
	</ol>
	</li>
	<li style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:19px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:list .5in"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">Click&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Next</span></strong>.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:19px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:list .5in"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">In the&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Parameter Summary</span></strong>&nbsp;tab, you can change the default values of the parameters. Follow the steps mentioned in the step 6 to edit the parameters.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:19px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:list .5in"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">Click&nbsp;Next.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:19px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:list .5in"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">If you do not want to enable the assignment immediately, clear the&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Enable Assignment(s)</span></strong>&nbsp;check box. You can then enable the assignment later using the&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Assignments &amp; Tuning</span></strong>&nbsp;pane.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:19px"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:list .5in"><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'><span style="color:#212529">Click&nbsp;<strong><span style='font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif'>Finish</span></strong>.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
</ol>
